title: Active Users
description: Number of users with at least one visit during the period, meaning the number of users during the period.

title: New Users
description: Number of users that start playing the game on this platform. These are users that were not playing the game in any other platform before.

title: Active Users Deprecated
description: Number of users with at least one visit to the game during the period, meaning the number of users playing the game during the period.
